    "description": "Step into a world of stark contrasts and mind-bending puzzles with Voidstepper. Immerse yourself in a uniquely stylized 2D platformer where the simplicity of pure black and white aesthetics belies the complexity of its challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096950/extras/79525f78e9a5b98f763e37433a567db7.avif?t=1758114472\" width=616 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>GRAVITY MANIPULATION</strong><br><br>You must defy the laws of physics by stepping into the Void. Enter the Void to discover new pathways, solve intricate puzzles, evade enemies and unlock hidden secrets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096950/extras/488d4afd69e37f0ca7d8e1f4eec7cf45.poster.avif?t=1758114472\" width=616 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096950/extras/488d4afd69e37f0ca7d8e1f4eec7cf45.webm?t=1758114472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096950/extras/488d4afd69e37f0ca7d8e1f4eec7cf45.mp4?t=1758114472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>DESTRUCTIBLE TERRAIN</strong><br><br>Utilize the environment to your advantage. Destroy any terrain to create barriers against deadly turrets and lasers, or carve your way to reach otherwise inaccessible heights. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096950/extras/afc50d023de1e27a26e298f1b889e292.poster.avif?t=1758114472\" width=616 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096950/extras/afc50d023de1e27a26e298f1b889e292.webm?t=1758114472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096950/extras/afc50d023de1e27a26e298f1b889e292.mp4?t=1758114472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Minimalist Art Style: Experience the elegance of pure black-and-white graphics that enhance the game's challenging and immersive nature.<br></li><li>Dynamic Puzzles: Engage with puzzles that require both brainpower and dexterity, offering a satisfying blend of cognitive and physical challenges.<br></li><li>Strategic Terrain Manipulation: Innovatively use destructible environments to block hazards, build paths, and create safe zones in real-time.</li></ul>",
